{"tid":365680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我真心建議大家去遊完行之後自首","createTime":"2017-08-19T12:20:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-20T13:06:40.000Z","uid":44925,"like":346,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5a534b38161631d94b75629f7a8248fa7a524048","tid":365680,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T12:20:34.000Z","msg":"講真，大家參加得佔中一定有犯法<br />\n犯左法，就要承擔罪責，先係良好公民<br />\n遊完行，表達完訴求，最好去警署自首<br />\n<br />\n不過為左爭加警方辦事效率，倒不如一齊去灣仔警察總部自首，就算唔自首，都可以指證其他人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過記住千祈唔好犯法<br />\n<br />\n雖然果度應該無咁大容納到當時參加人數<br />\n咁容納唔到最多咪逼啲囉，最多逼出去少少<br />\n記得叫多啲人黎守法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />維護法治，你我有責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n反正全香港人都有罪<br />\n如果律政司唔肯檢控哂十萬人<br />\n記住一定要一齊上門搵佢地要求檢控<br />\n有咩理由得咁少人坐先"},{"pid":"0631e0bf4a8f9198560f7ac5b6d5d0bf9d8ac306","tid":365680,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T12:21:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講真，大家參加得佔中一定有犯法<br />\n犯左法，就要承擔罪責，先係良好公民<br />\n遊完行，表達完訴求，最好去警署自首<br />\n<br />\n不過為左增加警方辦事效率，倒不如一齊去灣仔警察總部自首，就算唔自首，都可以指證其他人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過記住千祈唔好犯法<br />\n<br />\n雖然果度應該無咁大容納到當時參加人數<br />\n咁容納唔到最多咪逼啲囉，最多逼出去少少<br />\n記得叫多啲人黎守法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />維護法治，你我有責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n反正全香港人都有罪<br />\n如果律政司唔肯檢控哂十萬人<br />\n記住一定要一齊上門搵佢地要求檢控<br />\n有咩理由得咁少人坐先</blockquote>"},{"pid":"2b72e1adf109aa364da0534c649959ba041644e0","tid":365680,"uid":68081,"like":12,"dislike":37,"score":-25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T12:22:29.000Z","msg":"最叻係你，留名等睇樓主自首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0f74716ffe92f77dc66cdd2d92a32a9b06a2991","tid":365680,"uid":44925,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T12:24:04.000Z","msg":"真心，要警方自己搵證據好辛苦<br />\n又要勞煩DOJ哂人力物力檢控<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自首係最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等佢一次過捉哂<br />\n<br />\n雖然香港監倉應該無咁大容納咁多人，唔緊要啦<br />\n實有地方既"},{"pid":"0f07d0baf45e005e177de3a7289e63a6afac6c06","tid":365680,"uid":65128,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T12:26:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9b7e494aeb8d84ee40a6697070bc6680adc503ec","tid":365680,"uid":44925,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T12:27:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最叻係你，留名等睇樓主自首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n遵守法律同協助警方係每個好市民責任"},{"pid":"1f8d350171dfbb5f4a8fde66f22366490457b42e","tid":365680,"uid":19557,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T12:28:47.000Z","msg":"呢個post 有兩個係block 左 即係有五毛 證明中共在意大家全部集體自首"},{"pid":"cc3527c087b1f1f4b7e3ddbb276d65f71ae03625","tid":365680,"uid":44925,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T12:29:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/19/202619_ff94c513f6050194117827d31dd67316.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F19%2F202619_ff94c513f6050194117827d31dd67316.jpg&h=6bfbc188&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n佔中暴徒咁多人，邊止咁少<br />\n得一個人千祈唔好自首<br />\n起碼搵夠一萬個先好去<br />\n<br />\n咁警方可以一次過做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n增加行政效率"},{"pid":"582487bdd5fe4c3ac4ba97c7c580c95f490f785e","tid":365680,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T12:29:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最叻係你，留名等睇樓主自首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a45f9339e95d58ddf45582995aff2c68c7e5be1a","tid":365680,"uid":63338,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T12:32:30.000Z","msg":"希望你唔係真心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5473c22c39a9c17f9bb25f07c7e34de1924c1ead","tid":365680,"uid":49955,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T12:33:55.000Z","msg":"覺得香港人唔敢玩自首<br />\n不過都幫你推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a51dea840d21669b198b71cd7130b9347fcd051","tid":365680,"uid":44925,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T12:33:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>希望你唔係真心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一個人既話唔好真心<br />\n多人既話可以真心"},{"pid":"0ff109dec271c01ea5134bb4e5a0f0ad3668f6e1","tid":365680,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T12:34:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個post 有兩個係block 左 即係有五毛 證明中共在意大家全部集體自首</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">呢個post 得我同樓主，你block 左二個，既是你block 左樓主囉，柒頭。數學都唔識學人上連登，怪不得叫柒頭雲海<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"f0e5c3b200575554f2bf84be9196c93afedd6a01","tid":365680,"uid":44925,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T12:35:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>覺得香港人唔敢玩自首<br />\n不過都幫你推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你叫你一個人企係條馬路中間你都唔敢<br />\n但佔中暴徒一大班係度，就係人都夠膽企出去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n毛主席名句：人多好辦事<br />\n永遠是對的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9597ed742c97e161497baf363f080a84523a796a","tid":365680,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T12:48:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f5eb55785e1e8d53bb047ff699d50764ed35002","tid":365680,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T12:53:51.000Z","msg":"推到俾暴徒首領睇到，望佢地良心發現"},{"pid":"dbf64aeb98ac544a8fcc6ab6c5add1b9301bab05","tid":365680,"uid":8009,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T13:04:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要返工"},{"pid":"f2999d561fc324adac7146e9f37e37c635ff81f6","tid":365680,"uid":51775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T13:54:47.000Z","msg":"有道理<br />\n推"},{"pid":"59d433a2d98584d2012987811df9d8e2116595a1","tid":365680,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T13:59:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最叻係你，留名等睇樓主自首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實佢咁講無錯，美國啱啱都集體排隊去警局自首塞爆佢<br />\n<br />\n如果有10幾萬人，去警察總部門口排隊自首又係一個上國際a1新聞嘅機會"},{"pid":"0fd13eec419dbd2c311c22362b22745815303ba7","tid":365680,"uid":44358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T14:03:38.000Z","msg":"係街執個一毫報警當失物做好市民重有益社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0586603e9bdd22b872b193a8dfde6c526fc306f5","tid":365680,"uid":51814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T14:09:23.000Z","msg":"全部老野坐監就解决哂土地房屋教育醫療就業問題，建制派仲唔去排隊自首。"},{"pid":"2572cb3bbe8fe6b595727f